                    p Millions of people are starving in Africa and the world at large because the demand for foods has overshot the supply. Invest”N”Farm is an AgriTech product that bridges the gap between the demand for food and its supply by partnering with farmers and landowners in Africa to create more farming opportunities. As a result, job opportunities are created, food production is increased and Return On Investment (ROI) is certain where supply is at par with demand.
