                    P As an AgriTech product, Invest”N”Farm makes it extremely easy for you to venture into the agricultural business terrain by using your mobile phone or PC. Being a digital agricultural investor opens you up to tremendous opportunities on a global scale all from the comfort of your home and digital devices.
             
                .col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12 
                    h5 DIVERSIFIED PORTFOLIO
                    p Invest”N”Farm does not limit your investment opportunities to only a few products. Our list of investment portfolios includes all cash crops and livestock. Moreover, our agricultural settlements are not limited to only one geographical area. We have plantations in different parts of the continent which creates more global opportunities to have a diversified portfolio in the Agricultural marketplace.
                .col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12 
                    h5 START WITH LITTLE FUNDS
                    p Invest”N”Farm has no minimum investment amount to get started. Start with what you have and watch your investment grow. All you have to do is fund your wallet and choose from any of our investment portfolios.    
        .container.d-none#slide2      
