                    p Invest”N”Farm runs on a Secure Socket Layer (SSL) that ensures that all messages transmitted from the site are encrypted. For mobile payments, Invest”N”Farm has integrated the Flutterwave payment gateway, which is highly secure. With Invest”N”Farm, your funds stay safe as our farms are insured and secured as a strategy for risk management.

